name: FEG BSC (OLD)
public_notice: FEG BSC (FEG) has migrated from their older contract to a new one. For more information, please view this announcement on Twitter and visit new token page here here.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.
